{
  "stem": "6763.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Sarajevo was definitely a camp, uh, more prepared for the amassing of more people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no open spaces where you could roam, uh, like in the camp before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were not told anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were just arrived there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, that was, that was it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Um, for no apparent reason about five days later, we were told that we would be leaving that camp and go further down to Bosnia, closer to down south to the Dalmatian coast area, but not-- we were not told where.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were just told we were going further south.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were put again on trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Um, and we were, we arrived in a city, Muslim city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, Sarajevo is a basically Muslim city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so is Mostar.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there, we arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Uh, I remember it was late afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were given stars to wear at that point, um, yellow star in the front and in the back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were walked from the railroad through the town to whatever destination.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's when I had the first experience of having stones thrown at me, and predominantly by kids shouting, you know dirty Jews, rotten Jews, uh, whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Um, they were not very large stones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But they were stones, nevertheless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were taken to a schoolhouse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was an empty schoolhouse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I remember there were closets in the classrooms, you know, like armoire-type of closets where teachers kept their supplies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I remember some of the men taking these closets and turning them down and putting them on the ground, and then taking the shelves out to make a bed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In other words, it was like almost an enclosure, to feel like, uh, some people were fighting over it.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
